      "note": "summary",
      "abstract": "Provides that additional taxes otherwise imposed upon disqualification of land from certain forestland special assessment programs may not be collected if the disqualification is due to the suspension of reforestation requirements as a result of insects or disease. Takes effect on the 91st day following adjournment sine die."
